Last week I lead the New Jersey delegation in a bipartisan letter insisting that significant support for the Postal Service be included in the next coronavirus package. 

The USPS will be instrumental in ensuring a safe, fair election this fall. Now is not the time to abandon it. https://t.co/uqyxPqc6jr

full_text:
I am proud that my office was able to support Frenchtown in securing this funding, and I will continue to fight each day in Congress to bring federal tax dollars back to New Jersey -TM 

https://t.co/Fk76Drq4OJ

He left an indelible mark on this committee and will be sorely missed. Today, we place flowers at his seat and honor his memory. https://t.co/gkyKEyIOxb

full_text: Elijah Cummings lived his life based on principle and patriotism and was a model for us all. In Congress he fought every day for the people of Baltimore and all Americans. His presence will be sorely missed. https://t.co/53ju8VORG7
